    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cube Railway is an exciting puzzle game that challenges players to strategically fit blocks to complete the construction of a railway track and allow the train to move forward. With 40 levels filled with increasingly challenging puzzles, each stage presents a specific number of available moves, making every decision crucial for success. If players fail to fit the blocks correctly within the move limit, the stage resets for a new attempt. The game features an original soundtrack that creates an immersive and captivating atmosphere, complemented by stunning low poly visuals that make the experience visually appealing and unique. With simple controls, Cube Railway is perfect for players of all ages looking for satisfying challenges in a charming setting. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 40 levels;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Original soundtrack;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Satisfying puzzles;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Low poly visuals;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play with the mouse.</p>",
